{
  "texts": [
    "While 21.8% of the respondents were neutral, 32.9% differed and 18.5% strongly differed with the opinion.",
    "The mean is 2.66 which is considered moderate.",
    "In the last item, no 28, 63% (SA 23.6 & A 39.4%) of the respondents said that their teachers took extra measures to enhance students\" English language skills.",
    "While 24.5% remained neutral, 9.7 differed, and 2.8% strongly differed.",
    "The mean is 3.71 which is considered high."
  ]
}